{
 "name": "RPlog_Serenella_and_Shael-The_Brawl",
 "title": "Serenella and Shael: The Brawl",
 "summary": "At a Vorzyd spaceport, the smuggler Shael is loading fragile cooling-unit parts aboard her ship when a heavily drugged Serenella Jordain tumbles out of the Margin and starts shoving her droids. The confrontation escalates into a brawl as the paranoid, raging Serenella tries to pry open Shael's crates, convinced she is hiding spice, while Shael desperately defends her cargo and trades insults. Despite her drugged state, the nimble dancer dodges most blows and eventually lands a solid punch to Shael's face, but the fight is broken up by Marine Lieutenant Vengan Draelis and his man Tarkis, who fires a warning shot and then a stun bolt that drops Serenella flat. Vengan arrests both women, reading them their rights and ordering a search of Shael's ship and cargo over her angry protests of innocence.",
